metadata.name: MusicCryptoPunks #1
metadata.description: This is a unique member of the MusicCryptoPunks Collection created to support music artists and producers. Each piece in the collection will come metal copy with a card of authenticity to hang in your home. Proof of purchase is needed to redeem your metal copy. Please send your proof of purchase and mailing information to Sales@mediacoinllc.com. Shipping costs may vary based on your mailing address. All collection holders will be informed of future music video productions, celebrity events, studio recording sessions, and artist meet and greets to be announced immediately following the close of our initial opening. All current collection owners will gain access to our Recording Studio to be created on the Metaverse in the near future.
